blockquote>無人會去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻啦，97前返大陸先正，物價夠平。d人又羡慕你香港人身份。<br />\n<br />\n幾百元可以玩幾日，十萬蚊可以買千呎樓。<br />\n<br />\n港男北上搵女朋友和老婆，比現在易千倍。<br />\n<br />\n現在，又貴，又成個香港咁。冇咩意思。"},{"pid":"2d33cf7aa870f40da0b27234471553fa8aeeca73","tid":432664,"uid":47027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過捉到真係會整個雞蟲印你嘆！</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳聞真係會stamp個們唯你本回鄉證度，雖然唔係叫雞蟲印，不過你老婆一定知，同判你打靶差唔多，依家轉咗卡，冇得睇，你瞞到你老婆十五日就過到骨。"},{"pid":"6a13320a80a34548daf3349e2c6cebc8a4d62bf5","tid":432664,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過捉到真係會整個雞蟲印你嘆！</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳聞真係會stamp個們唯你本回鄉證度，雖然唔係叫雞蟲印，不過你老婆一定知，同判你打靶差唔多，依家轉咗卡，冇得睇，你瞞到你老婆十五日就過到骨。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你出國，你本 passport 一樣姐。<br />\n都係要蓋印。<br />\n99年出回鄉卡，02年開始唔在舊回鄉證中蓋印"},{"pid":"8f89300a13cba71c9626fed3cc4bd711ff09b5b3","tid":432664,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ff95dfa766a3f0f894ebc947a99ae72f19f8c23","tid":432664,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NNR4Tbc6XQk&amp;t=132s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNNR4Tbc6XQk%26t%3D132s&d=CkoTydT07GA4d35S6NBSJDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e6f23cbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NNR4Tbc6XQk&amp;t=132s</a>"}]}